569
00:34:58,420 --> 00:35:00,780
 Nema Bože jako je tvoja volja.

570
00:35:00,780 --> 00:35:02,120
 Da, da, ne, to je moja.

571
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,360
 Ja to želim postići

572
00:35:03,360 --> 00:35:05,260
 i ovo su prakse kojima ću ja to postići.

573
00:35:05,260 --> 00:35:07,280
 Htio Bože ti to ili ne htio?

574
00:35:07,280 --> 00:35:07,960
 Hvorilo, gvorilo.

575
00:35:07,960 --> 00:35:10,860
 Ili zanemarajući opće Boga u cijeloj priči.

576
00:35:10,860 --> 00:35:13,060
 Ja sam ga, ja bih rekao,

577
00:35:13,060 --> 00:35:15,920
 u svojim praksama nesvjesno zanemarivao,

578
00:35:16,060 --> 00:35:19,220
 jer, kažem, nisam znao.

579
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:19,500
 Dobro.

580
00:35:19,500 --> 00:35:20,680
 Tako ja bih rekao da puno ljudi

581
00:35:20,680 --> 00:35:21,620
 koji su u tim praksama

582
00:35:21,620 --> 00:35:23,600
 često ne znaju da čine zlo.

583
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,100
 Da ulaze u područje,

584
00:35:25,100 --> 00:35:27,100
 da ih je džava jednostavno zavarao,

585
00:35:27,100 --> 00:35:29,420
 ponudio im to kao nešto dobro,

586
00:35:29,420 --> 00:35:32,680
 a možda jako bitan dio za nas kršćane,

587
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:34,120
 osobi to katolike koji gledamo,

588
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:35,140
 koji gledaju ovo,

589
00:35:35,140 --> 00:35:38,860
 u nedostatku svjetlih primjera,

590
00:35:38,860 --> 00:35:40,040
 svjedočanstva vjere.

591
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:42,480
 Znači ja sam poprlično siguran

592
00:35:42,480 --> 00:35:44,080
 da je moj život potpuno drugačije izgledao

593
00:35:44,080 --> 00:35:45,220
 da sam imao jednu osobu,

594
00:35:45,820 --> 00:35:47,340
 samo jednu koja mi je bila dovoljno bliska,

595
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,820
 a koja je ozbiljno uzimala vjeru

596
00:35:49,820 --> 00:35:50,820
 i živjela vjeru.

597
00:35:50,820 --> 00:35:51,760
 Koja je molila za mene

598
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:53,580
 i kad sam zapravo se okružio ljudima

599
00:35:53,580 --> 00:35:54,940
 koji su krenuli moliti za mene,

600
00:35:54,940 --> 00:35:56,080
 koji su živjeli vjeru,

601
00:35:56,080 --> 00:35:57,440
 to me privuklo jako.

602
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:59,480
 I to me izbavilo iz tih hralja

603
00:35:59,480 --> 00:36:00,800
 do toga čemu doći.

604
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:00,980
 Ok.

605
00:36:00,980 --> 00:36:03,880
 Zgoda sa egipatskim boženostvima.

606
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:05,260
 Mislim, koliko može biti zgoda?

607
00:36:05,260 --> 00:36:06,620
 Da, da, nezgoda.

608
00:36:06,620 --> 00:36:09,300
 Nezgodna zgoda, zvana nezgoda.

609
00:36:12,180 --> 00:36:12,920
 Postoje jedno,

610
00:36:12,920 --> 00:36:15,380
 postoje dva Hermesa

611
00:36:15,380 --> 00:36:18,480
 u kontekstu božanstava.

612
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:20,260
 Možemo reći demona, ali božanstava.

613
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:20,500
 Dobro.

614
00:36:20,500 --> 00:36:21,780
 Jedan je grčki Hermes.

615
00:36:21,780 --> 00:36:22,380
 Dobro.

616
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:26,460
 Mislim da on bio nešto,

617
00:36:26,460 --> 00:36:27,700
 glasnik neki, tako nešto.

618
00:36:27,700 --> 00:36:27,980
 Dobro.

619
00:36:27,980 --> 00:36:29,780
 I ima egipatski Hermes.

620
00:36:29,780 --> 00:36:32,280
 Tako zvani Hermes Trismegistos.

621
00:36:32,280 --> 00:36:34,060
 Tri puta najveći Hermes.

622
00:36:34,060 --> 00:36:34,400
 Dobro.

623
00:36:34,400 --> 00:36:38,300
 Tako se naziva, kao, jel?

624
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:42,500
 I on je bio kao bog psihičke magije.

625
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:43,680
 Tako je me zanimalo, jel?

626
00:36:43,680 --> 00:36:44,120
 Dobro.

627
00:36:44,120 --> 00:36:45,560
 Zadužen za psihičku magiju u Egiptu, jel?

628
00:36:47,500 --> 00:36:52,240
 I on mi je bio od tih božanstava i tih nekih stvari,

629
00:36:52,240 --> 00:36:54,160
 Bož mi prosti, najdražiji.

630
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:56,660
 U smislu, najviše sam se njemu utjecao.

631
00:36:56,660 --> 00:37:00,940
 To je prakse koje njega spominju ulazi u to.

632
00:37:00,940 --> 00:37:05,940
 I ja sam se obratio, znači, 2010. godine.

633
00:37:05,940 --> 00:37:08,140
 I dubio ću vam pričati o tome, ali...

634
00:37:08,140 --> 00:37:11,240
 Na katoličanstvo, da, da, da.

635
00:37:11,240 --> 00:37:15,660
 Na kršćanstvo, pa katoličanstvo, možemo i o tome.

636
00:37:15,660 --> 00:37:17,760
 Koliko si rekao, pet sati treba podkast?

637
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:18,380
 Da, da, pet.

638
00:37:18,380 --> 00:37:21,900
 Obično pet, to je prosjek, da treba možemo i duže.

639
00:37:21,900 --> 00:37:22,420
 E, dobro.

640
00:37:22,420 --> 00:37:23,600
 Probat ćemo ajde upljati.

641
00:37:23,600 --> 00:37:23,880
 Dobro.

642
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:30,920
 I bio sam, već sam tad ušao u zajednstvu na novorođeni.

643
00:37:30,920 --> 00:37:32,420
 Bio sam jedno na molitvi.

644
00:37:32,420 --> 00:37:33,500
 Čekaj, čekaj, čekaj, čekaj.

645
00:37:33,500 --> 00:37:37,980
 Znači, obratio sam se na kršćanstvo, pa poslije katoličanstvo.

646
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,380
 Pa prošlo je još pet godina.

647
00:37:39,380 --> 00:37:45,380
 I onda sam došao na molitvu kod velečasnog Ivice i Matije našeg.

648
00:37:45,380 --> 00:37:47,880
 I još je bila i stana.

649
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:51,480
 I molili su za mene po fazama života.

650
00:37:51,480 --> 00:37:55,200
 Mislim da je sati nešto trala molitva, gdje su u redom molili.

651
00:37:55,200 --> 00:37:57,480
 Mislim da smo došli do rođenja, nismo došli dalje.

652
00:37:57,480 --> 00:38:00,440
 Inače, preporučam svima, molitva po fazama života,

653
00:38:00,440 --> 00:38:03,340
 bilo polazlje osobno ili uz neće vodstvo.

654
00:38:03,340 --> 00:38:06,280
 Mio Barada najviše to propagira.

655
00:38:07,940 --> 00:38:12,000
 I prolazili su tako, molili su za mene, kao zagovorna molitva,

656
00:38:12,000 --> 00:38:15,320
 gdje smo prolazili po fazama života.

657
00:38:15,320 --> 00:38:18,320
 Znači, od mog začeća, pa preko prvi mjesec, utrudnoći,

658
00:38:18,320 --> 00:38:19,600
 mamin, drugi, treći i tako.

659
00:38:19,600 --> 00:38:21,080
 I sve do rođenja.

660
00:38:21,080 --> 00:38:25,280
 I u jednom trenutku Matija, koji ima jako izražen dar spoznaje,

661
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:27,100
 je zastoj rekao je,

662
00:38:28,100 --> 00:38:30,600
 osjećam da nešto blokira molitvu.

663
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:35,740
 Nešto mi je kao neki trisim ego, trimi sego.

664
00:38:35,740 --> 00:38:37,480
 Ja kažem, možda trismegistos.

665
00:38:37,480 --> 00:38:39,020
 I on kaže, da, da, to.

666
00:38:39,020 --> 00:38:40,100
 I on ne ježi se onako.

667
00:38:40,100 --> 00:38:41,280
 Ja se isto ne ježio.

668
00:38:42,160 --> 00:38:45,060
 Neugodno, kaže, da, možda, Hermes trismegistos.

669
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:48,700
 Kaže, da, moguće da je to duh ili zloduh koji blokira molitvu,

670
00:38:48,700 --> 00:38:49,960
 jer sam se njemu utjecu.

671
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:53,420
 I to je, znači, ja sam živio vjeru tri, četiri godine tada, pet,

672
00:38:53,420 --> 00:38:56,000
 ali još uvijek su ostali neki ostaci.

673
00:38:56,000 --> 00:38:58,160
 U duhovnom svijetu to je sve aktualno.

674
00:38:58,160 --> 00:39:01,440
 Da, da, dok se ne odreknemo nečeg, dok se ne pokajemo,

675
00:39:01,440 --> 00:39:02,980
 dok ne u isov ime ne potjeramo.

676
00:39:02,980 --> 00:39:05,360
 I onda je on rekao vele častnom ivici,

677
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:08,600
 ajde ti moli da svežeš tog duha, Hermes trismegistosa.

678
00:39:08,600 --> 00:39:11,160
 Ja sam se tog, naravno, odrekao, jer sveg tog se i prije odrekao,

679
00:39:11,160 --> 00:39:13,840
 ali ovo je bio complete package, onako,

680
00:39:13,840 --> 00:39:17,420
 ono, detaljno očišćenje, ajmo reći, duše tog područja,

681
00:39:17,420 --> 00:39:20,100
 gdje onda sam se ja odrekao i pokajao,

682
00:39:20,100 --> 00:39:23,680
 i on je molio da se svežeš i odiđe od mene

683
00:39:23,680 --> 00:39:25,620
 taj duh Hermesa trismegistosa.

684
00:39:25,620 --> 00:39:28,600
 Od tada nemam problema s njim, koliko znam,

685
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:33,640
 ali evo, to pokazuje i na tu duhovnu dimenziju jednu,

686
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:36,040
 gdje je, ono, poprvo je specifično,

687
00:39:36,040 --> 00:39:37,240
 jesli ti kad čuo trismegistosa?

688
00:39:37,240 --> 00:39:37,380
 Ne.

689
00:39:38,040 --> 00:39:40,480
 i sad oni u molitvi mu je došlo baš tako...

690
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:42,060
 E, to mi je fascinantno da je iščupo to.

691
00:39:42,060 --> 00:39:44,120
 E, da, da, meni je bilo isto fascinantno.

692
00:39:44,120 --> 00:39:45,860
 U jednu ruku sam se, ono, stresao kao malo,

693
00:39:45,860 --> 00:39:48,620
 a ne bih rekao plašio, ali, ono, scimalo me,

694
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:51,060
 a u drugu ruku sam bio kao,

695
00:39:51,060 --> 00:39:52,740
 wow, Bože, stvarno si precizan.

696
00:39:52,740 --> 00:39:58,160
 I, ono, Bogu hvala na tom daru u mati

697
00:39:58,160 --> 00:39:59,700
 koji trenutno tad se bio očitovao,

698
00:39:59,700 --> 00:40:03,140
 da, kao snajper na cilja, šta je problem?

699
00:40:03,140 --> 00:40:04,840
 Dobro, ali rekao si da si,

700
00:40:04,840 --> 00:40:06,940
 to je egipatsko božanstvo,

701
00:40:07,000 --> 00:40:08,520
 da si jako

702
00:40:08,520 --> 00:40:10,460
 stremio ka njemu, dakle,

703
00:40:10,460 --> 00:40:13,180
 s obzirom na

704
00:40:13,180 --> 00:40:14,960
 na to zašto je bilo glavno,

705
00:40:14,960 --> 00:40:16,540
 ta magija

706
00:40:16,540 --> 00:40:18,120
 na razini psihe,

707
00:40:18,120 --> 00:40:20,920
 dokud si došao

708
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:22,960
 i zašto si, očito si se još bavio

709
00:40:22,960 --> 00:40:24,420
 drugim stvarima, zašto si

710
00:40:24,420 --> 00:40:26,820
 prebacio fokus sa toga na nešto drugo?

711
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:28,340
 je li te nešto falilo, je li te nešto

712
00:40:28,340 --> 00:40:30,280
 zainterigiralo, je si općenito ono...

713
00:40:30,280 --> 00:40:32,340
 To je bilo, ja bih rekao,

714
00:40:32,340 --> 00:40:35,100
 kombinacija prisutna kad sam se bavio tim praksama,

715
00:40:35,100 --> 00:40:36,340
 prije obraćenja, kad sam se obratio,

716
00:40:36,340 --> 00:40:37,540
 sam srezao to sve skupa,

717
00:40:38,380 --> 00:40:40,900
 ali prije samo sam nadodavao

718
00:40:40,900 --> 00:40:41,780
 jednu na drugu stvar,

719
00:40:41,780 --> 00:40:43,200
 jer u New Age-u...

720
00:40:43,200 --> 00:40:44,420
 I što oni sve trpe jedno drugo?

721
00:40:44,420 --> 00:40:45,480
 Sve trpe jedno drugo, da.

722
00:40:45,480 --> 00:40:47,780
 Čak i kabala koja ima

723
00:40:47,780 --> 00:40:49,380
 poveznicu sa židovstvom,

724
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:51,060
 znači Torom, znači starim zavjetom,

725
00:40:51,060 --> 00:40:53,560
 gdje onda je jedna od praksi,

726
00:40:53,560 --> 00:40:54,840
 to te vjerojatno zanima,

727
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:57,900
 bila kao...

728
00:40:57,900 --> 00:40:59,480
 Bilo je nekoliko tih praksi,

729
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:01,040
 neke su bile istočaške,

730
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:02,020
 neke su bile te kabale,

731
00:41:02,020 --> 00:41:03,440
 neke su bile te psiške magije,

732
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:04,400
 egipatske, kako god,

733
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:05,880
 i onda bilo je to nek...

734
00:41:05,880 --> 00:41:06,780
 Znači vezano za auru,

735
00:41:06,780 --> 00:41:08,260
 znači povačavaš si auru,

736
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:10,260
 pa onda vježbe disanja, meditacije,

737
00:41:10,260 --> 00:41:12,480
 i bila je jedna...

738
00:41:12,480 --> 00:41:14,360
 Tu je počelo i mantranje, isto?

739
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:15,340
 Kaj mantranje?

740
00:41:15,340 --> 00:41:18,420
 Mantranje, znači ponavljanje istih riječi,

741
00:41:18,420 --> 00:41:22,420
 kako bi postigo neko stanje duha.

742
00:41:22,420 --> 00:41:25,380
 Zapravo je to često zazivanje

743
00:41:25,380 --> 00:41:27,160
 lažnih božanstva.

744
00:41:27,700 --> 00:41:29,260
 Konkretno, znači mantra ko sam ja govorio,

745
00:41:29,260 --> 00:41:31,100
 je bilo, smiješno je,

746
00:41:31,100 --> 00:41:32,300
 nikad nisam bio u Hare Krišnama,

747
00:41:32,300 --> 00:41:34,120
 ali je bilo Hare Krišna i Hare Rama,

748
00:41:34,120 --> 00:41:35,760
 što su tri božanstva.

749
00:41:35,760 --> 00:41:37,320
 Hare Krišna i Rama, valjda.

750
00:41:37,320 --> 00:41:38,660
 Krišna i Rama sigurno,

751
00:41:38,660 --> 00:41:40,400
 a Hare ne znam da li je nešto.

752
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:41,620
 Znam da negleskom zec,

753
00:41:41,620 --> 00:41:43,300
 ali vjerojatno nije u tom kontekstu,

754
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:44,560
 nego je...

755
00:41:44,560 --> 00:41:46,700
 A oni Hare Krišna su poznati

756
00:41:46,700 --> 00:41:47,660
 po tome da mantraju to.

757
00:41:47,660 --> 00:41:50,980
 I to je vezano za taj dio joge,

758
00:41:50,980 --> 00:41:52,260
 kojim sam se počeo baviti

759
00:41:52,260 --> 00:41:53,480
 u tom sklopu New Age-a,

760
00:41:53,740 --> 00:41:54,860
 je bilo i to mantranje.

761
00:41:54,860 --> 00:41:58,100
 A dio tih prakse je bilo,

762
00:41:58,100 --> 00:41:59,460
 ne znam, ponavljanje.

763
00:41:59,460 --> 00:42:01,940
 Dio tog mogu ponoviti,

764
00:42:01,940 --> 00:42:03,460
 jer nije nužno loše.

765
00:42:03,460 --> 00:42:05,260
 Ono, ispred mene je Mihajl,

766
00:42:05,260 --> 00:42:06,240
 kao Arkanđeo Mihajl.

767
00:42:06,240 --> 00:42:06,520
 Dobro.

768
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:09,460
 Iza mene je Gabriel,

769
00:42:09,460 --> 00:42:10,340
 pored mene Rafael

770
00:42:10,340 --> 00:42:11,960
 i onda još četvrti neki je spomenut,

771
00:42:11,960 --> 00:42:13,840
 kojeg ne bi...

772
00:42:13,840 --> 00:42:15,720
 Možda je legit Arkanđeo,

773
00:42:15,720 --> 00:42:17,300
 jer ga spominja židlovska prede,

774
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:18,240
 ali ne znamo, evo.

775
00:42:18,240 --> 00:42:22,220
 Ali kažem, nije u kršanskom kanonu

776
00:42:22,220 --> 00:42:23,920
 ili da sad često se spominja.

777
00:42:23,920 --> 00:42:25,540
 Dobro, daj mi reći od svih tih...

778
00:42:25,540 --> 00:42:27,460
 Znači, govorimo o tome da si ti to,

779
00:42:27,460 --> 00:42:28,960
 osim što si čito o tome,

780
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:31,640
 učio...

781
00:42:31,640 --> 00:42:32,300
 Prakticirao.

782
00:42:32,300 --> 00:42:33,540
 Prakticirao si.

783
00:42:33,540 --> 00:42:37,040
 Sad zanima, ok, kuđim, pokušavaš doma,

784
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,960
 vjerojatno, nakon što pročitaš,

785
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:40,620
 pa mantraš, pa izučavaš,

786
00:42:40,620 --> 00:42:43,480
 pa jesi ikad negdje otišen

787
00:42:43,480 --> 00:42:45,700
 na neki oficijalni sastalak?

788
00:42:45,700 --> 00:42:46,940
 Da, nažalost, da.

789
00:42:46,940 --> 00:42:49,820
 I srečom,

790
00:42:49,820 --> 00:42:51,680
 Bog me zahvatio prije nego što sam nastavio

791
00:42:51,680 --> 00:42:52,220
 ići dalje.

792
00:42:52,220 --> 00:42:56,420
 Kako se često događa

793
00:42:56,420 --> 00:42:59,340
 da kad nas nešto počne zanimati,

794
00:42:59,340 --> 00:43:01,880
 počne nas to privlačiti

795
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:04,000
 i na neki način počnemo naletavat

796
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:04,560
 na tako neke stvari.

797
00:43:04,560 --> 00:43:05,920
 To mi je isto, to mi je isto nevjerojatno.

798
00:43:05,920 --> 00:43:07,900
 Mislim, meni se čini pogotovo tad

799
00:43:07,900 --> 00:43:09,780
